headline: Elliptic powers risk intelligence for BVNK's Layer1 - enabling stablecoin payments, trading and settlement at scale
summary: Elliptic, the global leader in digital asset decisioning, has partnered with BVNK to integrate Elliptic Lens into Layer1, the firm's stablecoin infrastructure for self-managed payments, enabling financial institutions to embed stablecoin flows with built-in risk intelligence and screening. Layer1 powers BVNK's platform and processes billions in payments each year, establishing itself as a trusted partner to fintechs, stablecoin issuers, and global payment providers.
